Troy M. Cloutier's Biography




			Our Chief Banking Officer, MidSouth Bancorp, Inc.; President and C.E.O., MidSouth Bank, N.A.  Mr. Cloutier brings knowledge of the day-to-day management of the Bank in his role as President & C.E.O. He was appointed to serve on the board effective January 1, 2017 to fill the vacancy created by the retirement of Will Charbonnet, Sr. Mr. Cloutier shall serve until the next shareholders' meeting held for the election of Class II directors. Mr. Cloutier is the son of Mr. C.R. Cloutier, the Company's President and C.E.O. and a Class I Director.
		
Source: MidSouth Bancorp, Inc. on 04/11/2017
		
	

 






